{"tid":1621251,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"今日改咗信伊斯蘭教/自由閪教嘅人入一入嚟","createTime":"2019-10-04T12:56:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-04T13:03:26.000Z","uid":327947,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"a16477599a208731d205a5d1a260342f79a7a2a2","tid":1621251,"uid":327947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T12:56:51.000Z","msg":"其實你哋點解要改信其他宗教？<br />\n如果你以宗教為理由而去戴口罩，你知唔知咁代表啲咩？<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">就係等同於你認同咗呢條法例！！！</span></span> 佢唔畀你帶，你就要讓步改信其他宗教？本身戴唔戴口罩就係我哋嘅自由，佢出個蒙面法話唔畀你帶你就唔帶？ 佢咁樣做嘅原因只有一個，只係想大家驚，從而減少示威者嘅人數，其實大家唔使驚。 佢越唔畀帶，你就越要帶！<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"> 大家要記住 一禁即反 絕不妥協！！！烏克蘭贏嘅原因都係因為咁</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人加油！！！</span></span>"},{"pid":"1243c1d7c7e5da606ed8d6409eb4e47717d10234","tid":1621251,"uid":327947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T12:58:45.000Z","msg":"推唔喐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44e39fbcd585f4780aae77a4e018c3a0ab109616","tid":1621251,"uid":327947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T12:59:58.000Z","msg":"自推1/10"},{"pid":"57f8c3cad5026dc93ae10cbf117be859769cc8e9","tid":1621251,"uid":327947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T13:00:15.000Z","msg":"自推2/10"},{"pid":"bc081248065d994781387b5a993ba5b08c318cb7","tid":1621251,"uid":327947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T13:02:13.000Z","msg":"自推3/10"},{"pid":"935ef861ad52a28dd630560e2b5d8d88a28eab11","tid":1621251,"uid":327947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T13:03:26.000Z"